snippet.title: Best VGM 1080 - El Shaddai - Tragic Scream
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Xbox 360 / PS3
El Shaddai : Ascension of the Metatron (2011)
Tragic Scream
Hayato Matsuo
